  "remarks": "\nViachaslau RASSALAI, is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) 2019. As the Deputy Minister of State Authority for Military Industry of the Republic of Belarus (SAMI) he has made available goods or technology that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
